struct vpsissCalBysOut

Field Documentation

uint32_t vpsissCalBysOut::copyStreamToEncode

TRUE configures, streams sent out on BYS out to be copied into encode

uint32_t vpsissCalBysOut::enable

TRUE, enables stream on BYS Out

uint32_t vpsissCalBysOut::freeRun

TRUE configures Bys out in Free running mode, False gated in idle

uint32_t vpsissCalBysOut::pixClock

Configure the pixel clock required. A non zero value will ensure that BYS ports pixel clock will be gated when idle.

uint32_t vpsissCalBysOut::xBlk

Configures the X blank to be inserted at end of line

uint32_t vpsissCalBysOut::yBlk

Configure the Y Blank to be inserted at end of frame
